Tableau has enterprise analytics platform solutions for deep data exploration. Create engaging visualizations, and embed them in your Lightning pages to use them in your workflows.

Tableau Cloud is a secure, fully hosted, cloud-based, self-service platform. Use it to prepare your data, author, analyze, collaborate, publish, and share.
Tableau Pulse allows you to make data-driven decisions right in your flow of work by sending you insights about metrics that you follow.
Tableau Desktop is a data visualization tool. Use the intuitive, drag-and-drop interface to discover hidden insights and make impactful business decisions.
Tableau Prep is a data preparation tool. Use it to clean, shape, and combine data for analysis in Tableau.
Tableau Server is a secure, on-premises solution for deploying Tableau in your own environment.

To learn more about Tableau products, go to Tableau Help.
